description:
Dive into this episode of DC Studios Showcase as Frankey Smith and Tyler Coates celebrate Black History Month, exploring Black heritage in DC comics, and talk DC romances for Valentine’s Day. Plus, James Adomian talks voicing Bane in the Max Original series Harley Quinn, blending comedy with menace, and shares unconventional relationship advice. 17:39 Valentine's Day and DC Relationships
22:50 James Adomian Interview 
27:17 Stand-Up Comedy and Voice Acting
